t scurried away like ants.);#if (ENGLISH,CHASING,RANGER) say(Run with your feeble bow, my breath shall catch you.);#if (ENGLISH,CHASING,ROGUE) say(You thought you could pilfer my corpse, rogue? What now do you think?.);#if (ENGLISH,CHASING,PET) say(I regret you tamed this animal, druid. It should not have been my enemy.);#if (ENGLISH,RETREATING) say(If I am saying this there is a bug, please call a GM. Oh, and Charnath hopes you die.);#if (ENGLISH,RETREATING) say(An Error Has Occurred: Please remain still until I regenerate enough to eat you.)#if (ENGLISH,ATTACKING,HUMAN) say(So, you face me. Brave. Brave and foolish.);#if (ENGLISH,ATTACKING,HUMAN) say(I remember times before your Gods were born, yet you still face me?);#if (ENGLISH,ATTACKING,HUMAN) say(My broods will enjoy feasting on your flesh.);#if (ENGLISH,ATTACKING,HUMAN) say(Your great grandfathers fought my sons and daughters, what chance have you?);#if (ENGLISH,ATTACKING,CLERIC) say(I met your Goddess, cleric. You are less worthy.);#if (ENGLISH,ATTACKING,WIZARD) say(I have lived in fires never sated, do you think you can hurt me?.);#if (ENGLISH,ATTACKING,WIZARD) say(Drop your reagents, they are foul to the taste.);#if (ENGLISH,ATTACKING,DRUID) say(I am master of all lizardkind, your tuskers and spiders do not scare me.);#if (ENGLISH,ATTACKING,FIGHTER) say(I learnt long ago that steel is to fools as water is to fish..);#if (ENGLISH,ATTACKING,RANGER) say(Your bow may be long ranger, but my neck is longer still.);#if (ENGLISH,ATTACKING,ROGUE) say(I cannot recall why I even bother with you.);#if (ENGLISH,ATTACKING,PET) say(Was this a friend to you, druid?.);#if (ENGLISH,ATTACKING,PET) say(This will feed my children this day.);#if (ENGLISH,KILLING,HUMAN) say(Predictable.);#if (ENGLISH,KILLING,HUMAN) say(When you have lived an aeon you may be more interesting.);#if (ENGLISH,KILLING,HUMAN) say(Regrettable that such a stupid species breeds so fast.);#if (ENGLISH,KILLING,HUMAN) say(I will be getting your pathetic garments out of my teeth for days...);#if (ENGLISH,KILLING,PET) say(Delicious. Have you any more?);#if (ENGLISH,HIDING,HUMAN) say(Hiding? It is your best option...);#if (ENGLISH,HIDING,HUMAN) say(Reveal yourself before I die of boredom.);#if (ENGLISH,HIDING,HUMAN) say(Come come, have you lost the will to die?);#if (ENGLISH,JUST_HID,HUMAN) say(Impressive, for an ant.);#if (ENGLISH,JUST_HID,HUMAN) say(I do so enjoy it when you realise you cannot win.);#if (ENGLISH,JUST_HID,HUMAN) say(Was that a potion, or is there something you can do well at?);// Weapon Effectiveness#dagger(50);#holydagger(50);#blooddagger(50);#broadsword(50);#katana(75);#scimitar(75);#flail(50);#mace(75);#warhammer(75);#spear(50);#sickle(75);#shortbow(50);#flamingsword(25);#frostaxe(125);// Creature Inventory// Inventory command:////  For grouped items, like potions://  #inventory(ITEM_NUMBER,MINIMUM,MAXIMUM);////  For ungrouped items, like weapons://  #inventory(ITEM_NUMBER,1,ODDS); // 1 in ODDS chance of carrying item#inventory(352,20,30); // 20 to 30 raw steaks#inventory(275,10,20); // 10 to 20 dragon teeth#inventory(379,15,25); // 15 to 25 dragon scales#inventory(515,0,1); //dragon egg